# Copiare in `apps/web/.env.local` (non committare). Vedi anche `../../.env.example`.
#
# --- Dev Windows / OneDrive (solo locale) ---
# `npm run dev` imposta NEXT_DIST_DIR=../.empathy-pro2-next-dev → output in apps/.empathy-pro2-next-dev/
# Non usare path assoluti in NEXT_DIST_DIR (Next 14: mkdir su apps\web\C:\... fallisce).
# Manuale: NEXT_DIST_DIR=../.empathy-pro2-next-dev, EMPATHY_PRO2_NO_WEBPACK_CACHE=1, WATCHPACK_POLLING=true
# Pulizia: npm run dev:clean. Vercel/deploy: vedi commento in root .env.example.
#
# Probe deploy: GET /api/health (pubblico, nessuna variabile).
# UI Settings (solo flag): GET /api/settings/integration-flags | Billing: /api/billing/checkout-config
# Integrazioni JSON (prod gated): GET /api/integrations/status + Authorization Bearer (INTEGRATIONS_STATUS_SECRET)
# Sitemap / URL canonici: opzionale; su Vercel si usa anche VERCEL_URL se assente.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://your-domain.example
# Indicizzazione: `0` = noindex (metadata, robots, header middleware) per preview/staging.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_INDEX=1
# Solo deploy HTTPS: abilita HSTS (header Strict-Transport-Security).
# NEXT_ENABLE_HSTS=1

# Supabase (SSR: middleware refresh + gate shell + `GET /api/auth/session`)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
# Solo server: inviti coach / accept (tabella coach_invitations). Dashboard → Settings → API → service_role
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=
# Dashboard → Authentication → URL configuration: aggiungi redirect
#   https://<host>/auth/callback
#   http://localhost:<porta>/auth/callback
# Magic link / OAuth usano `emailRedirectTo` → `/auth/callback?next=...`
#
# Org multitenant (coach↔atleta). Opzionale: se assente si usa lo seed `00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000001`
# (migration `000_pro2_orgs.sql`). In client (browser) usa il mirror pubblico se cambi org:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_EMPATHY_COACH_ATHLETES_ORG_ID=xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx
# EMPATHY_COACH_ATHLETES_ORG_ID=xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx

# --- Stripe (allineato a V1 `nextjs-empathy-pro` — stessi nomi variabile) ---
# Dashboard: https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys
# Webhook: https://YOUR_DOMAIN/api/webhooks/stripe  (verifica firma + log; persistenza come V1 da aggiungere)
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...   # o sk_live_... — solo server, mai nel client
# STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...   # o pk_live_... (Checkout Elements / client)
#
# Price ID mensili EUR (V1: `lib/billing/stripe-price-ids.ts` + `lib/account/plan-catalog.ts`)
# STRIPE_PRICE_SILVER_EUR=price_...
# STRIPE_PRICE_GOLD_EUR=price_...
# STRIPE_PRICE_COACH_ELITE_EUR=price_...
# STRIPE_PRICE_COACH_PRO_EUR=price_...
# STRIPE_PRICE_COACH_OLIMPIC_EUR=price_...
#
# Redirect Checkout (default Pro 2: `/pricing`; V1 usa spesso `/settings?billing=…`)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_CHECKOUT_SUCCESS_PATH=/pricing?billing=success
# NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_CHECKOUT_CANCEL_PATH=/pricing?billing=cancel
#
# Abilita POST /api/billing/checkout-session senza utente (solo demo/staging — non in prod senza rate limit / auth)
# STRIPE_CHECKOUT_ANON_ENABLED=1
# Trial giorni per subscription anonima (opzionale; es. allineamento V1 ~15)
# STRIPE_CHECKOUT_TRIAL_DAYS=15
#
# Pro 2 — CTA opzionale su /pricing (Payment Link hosted, solo pubblico, solo HTTPS)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_STRIPE_PAYMENT_LINK=https://buy.stripe.com/...

# LogMeal (solo server)
# LOGMEAL_API_KEY=
# LOGMEAL_API_BASE_URL=

# Spline
# SPLINE_SCENE_BASE_URL=

# Produzione: abilita GET /api/integrations/status solo con header
# Authorization: Bearer <stesso valore> (variabile solo server, non committare).
# INTEGRATIONS_STATUS_SECRET=
